{"tid":1300453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重申】要獨立調查委員會","createTime":"2019-07-09T11:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T08:40:17.000Z","uid":87915,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ffbfb2f8d7112acd2f67b8bccda4d03f7b439c9d","tid":1300453,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:15:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n屌你老母  我講咗三日啦 <br />\n仲係見到五大訴求  甚至七大訴求<br />\n<br />\n我屌哂你地老母<br />\n<br />\n唔係話其他訴求唔重要  但首要一定係獨立調查委員會 要求人係一定靠委員會呀<br />\n<br />\n社會要集中議題先有力量！<br />\n<br />\n睇吓林彥邦分析啦</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCredit: 林彥邦<br />\n<br />\n「壽終正寢」背後<br />\n<br />\n千呼萬喚，潛水多時的林鄭月娥終於再次回應，將「暫緩」變成「壽終正寢」，當然鬧聲一片。<br />\n<br />\n眾所周知，立法會程序，已提交的條例草案，只有押後和撤回，「暫緩」、「壽終正寢」都只是等同押後，隨時可以重上大會二讀，相信外界都對林鄭這一堆明顯經過細心雕琢的文字遊戲憤恨不已，但這部份其實無甚可談，甚至可以大膽估計，政府是預料到這些反應下，仍要出來「壽終正寢」。<br />\n<br />\n不是說撤回與否不重要，而是正如林鄭所言，「撤回」都可以在幾個月內重啟，拒絕「撤回」當然代表了政府以至北京，堅拒正面接納示威者條件的心理狀態，但對他們而言，更重要而不希望成為焦點的agenda，是無論如何，都不會成立獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n如果以常理分析，民間的五大訴求，最易做到的是那一個？<br />\n<br />\n答案當然是成立獨立調查委員會，畢毫，調查只是針對警方，將警方作為棄子切割，應該足以將民間怨氣減半，逢部份建制派如謝偉銓，都曾去信林鄭促請成立「獨立檢討委員會」，田北辰、鍾國斌、陳健波等都有類似意見，他們和民主派唯一的分別是，「兩邊都要查」，即調查不單針對警方，亦要調查示威者，講到底，就是成立調查委員會也無不可。<br />\n<br />\n獨立調查委員會的重要性不用多說，現行制度有幾廢不用多解釋，監警會無傳召證人權力、投訴警察課自己人查自己人等等，只有獨立調查委員會才有能力還原真相，到底是誰下令暴力鎮壓612、警方的處理有何不當，以至建制派所指，示威者的資金從何以來（咪香港人自己，低能）都會找到答案，更重要的是，警方近年持續的系統性濫權會受到重挫，沸騰的民怨會得以安撫。<br />\n<br />\n但政府完全不考慮、不接受。<br />\n<br />\n合理的解釋，是在政府的判斷中，警方必不可失，因為警察已經成為了唯一可以維持政權的槍。<br />\n<br />\n所以，政府會在民意對警方執法極度不滿下，閉門會見四個警察協會，表揚警方的表現；所以，政府會默許警方發投訴信予立法會主席，無視他們違反警隊政治中立的要求，更默許他們發信投訴英國國會議員，直接介入連香港政府本身都不敢觸碰的外交事務；所以政府會默許警方完全違反警例的執法行為：不帶委任證、隨意威嚇市民、動用過量武力等等。<br />\n<br />\n政府的判斷是，若失去警隊的支持，沒有了這把不問情由只聽命令的槍，特區政府根本無法管治下去，林鄭這個特首亦當不下去，若警察「兵變」，林鄭必定玩完。<br />\n<br />\n一個缺乏民意授權、缺乏認受性、連管治集團內部都分崩離析（你睇下CY集團搞緊咩？），所謂「文人政府」已經完全失去管治能力，必須要靠槍桿子維持政權，本質上其實和軍政府已無太大分別，或者至少已經肯定是police state。<br />\n<br />\n這種必須死攬警方的思維，才是「壽終正寢」背後的特區政府思維。<br />\n<br />\n若果竟然有警方人員能讀到這裡，誠意希望你想想，政府現下對警方的「支持」到底是甚麼一回事。是真心覺得警方「正義」，還是拿警方作為壓制反對聲音的武器？若果覺得警方成為磨心，誰是始作俑者，誰要負最大責任？是每天站在你背後講粗口的示威者、還是站在你背後、口說支持你卻一再用你的身軀躲避責難的人？"},{"pid":"02df60a17d5ee1f9742819195c177815e7abcf7f","tid":1300453,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:15:37.000Z","msg":"推9你老母呀"},{"pid":"ea17fd79e70bd7474b2ce47441a903028e914a81","tid":1300453,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:16:21.000Z","msg":"Push your mother"},{"pid":"453f0e98a498d55ef302f2c45cbfddb6d2c7b2ea","tid":1300453,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:17:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f2d7d00d296af2f00db7754a6f89401007c7e9f","tid":1300453,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:17:33.000Z","msg":"屌你呀  <br />\n<br />\n你地睇到未呀     獨立調查呀"},{"pid":"64d82d880bbb2557169b4af6a626a9d46165540a","tid":1300453,"uid":277137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:18:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99ec5d14602d954b7a99dc72f12e5e5c50291051","tid":1300453,"uid":131663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:18:17.000Z","msg":"啱丫，推"},{"pid":"da7923ec03882b258280d925be76cb6f0f946698","tid":1300453,"uid":147888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:18:29.000Z","msg":"要求設立獨立調查委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d9362ca972ace9288f9884c956def4612a328ee","tid":1300453,"uid":277137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:19:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79994666aed01af4470b31590ff158ce30d00df1","tid":1300453,"uid":87915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:20:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">比柒婆個壽終正寢 搞到離撚哂罩  係咪on9 架你地<br />\n<br />\n我地要獨立調查呀</span>"},{"pid":"143f5bd2bb5832be81c1a33919de35a8f2060cb6","tid":1300453,"uid":264771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:20:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a58ae8e63b539ac4e7af458063d648fdcbb5f95","tid":1300453,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ed071b2a8f1b4d123e975ceeadbda1e6ad03a3","tid":1300453,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:20:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a99e9f2ca21d4b2c181cce570e9ee0964dd75bb1","tid":1300453,"uid":87915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:22:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">學界又係唔撚識玩架<br />\n一個前題  獨立調查委員會 就公開會談<br />\n<br />\n個政府要迫9佢架</span>"},{"pid":"c2d1de90b215e6d277e23e8269ba215bfe8f7075","tid":1300453,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:22:30.000Z","msg":"《一日爭取唔到真普選，我地永遠處於被動》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"98c796aefebd3b753de727c631719cb429ae9719","tid":1300453,"uid":264457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:23:07.000Z","msg":"我半日前因為林鄭話「壽終正寢」已講左要獨立調查委員會針對黑警濫權。但大多數都負評我。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭5大訴求回應理性討論<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dgpsMS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dgpsMS</a>"},{"pid":"685c4405eba20c9396e881414150bdb95bd23031","tid":1300453,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2d1de90b215e6d277e23e8269ba215bfe8f7075","tid":1300453,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:22:30.000Z","msg":"《一日爭取唔到真普選，我地永遠處於被動》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:25:51.000Z","msg":"真普選太遙遠呀。<br />\n<br />\n我要獨立調查委員會呀！"},{"pid":"cee53183e4e46bd8812d6fa15e4d6517957a3405","tid":1300453,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:28:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a164cd71698b95ea3f01f3c38f3ba165241dad0b","tid":1300453,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:28:57.000Z","msg":"釋放義士先係最重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地喺出面開開心心查黑警，佢地喺監倉入面坐十年？人血饅頭咩<br />\n同埋講到尾告人都係律政司負責<br />\n唔換自己人上去做特首，獨立調查委員會好可能只係無牙老虎"},{"pid":"434bb46c2f7579ed0b58325b756a02df378f50e5","tid":1300453,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:31:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03d7e4488153f78c2bc1606d6f4633638db3d67c","tid":1300453,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:32:36.000Z","msg":"獨立委員會一定要有<br />\n你無下下就比班黑犬暴打<br />\n將來點行使公民權<br />\n記者第四權會比黑犬切割"},{"pid":"238907de2194fde26abfa7ba9926d077e93a000d","tid":1300453,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a164cd71698b95ea3f01f3c38f3ba165241dad0b","tid":1300453,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:28:57.000Z","msg":"釋放義士先係最重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地喺出面開開心心查黑警，佢地喺監倉入面坐十年？人血饅頭咩<br />\n同埋講到尾告人都係律政司負責<br />\n唔換自己人上去做特首，獨立調查委員會好可能只係無牙老虎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:33:12.000Z","msg":"why not both"},{"pid":"91ee77ddf40e9c2875c5ca428e2e3094aef37486","tid":1300453,"uid":265066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q3iJM1s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ3iJM1s.jpg&h=a4c4c6d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a10e9ed0cb063763c248bb789b8a989b36fff1e0","tid":1300453,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:38:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8612b338f6090dc99c12778ac23e068e1dd73bea"